::KitKat::

She watched the trees go by in a blurr as she ran along.
"Well, He kind of has a liking to Stringtra.  He just treats her a 
little different than the others.  He smiles more around her.  His 
voice softens when he talks to her.  If I didn't know any better, I'd 
call that puppy love."
